GeneralComments:
6am - 11pm, 7 days
Pak'N'Save Petone (in conjunction with Wellington Electricity) have installed two J1772 EV charging points and dedicated EV car parks towards the McDonalds end of the store. These are available free of charge for customer use while shopping in store. Please note a 60 minute time restriction is in place and use will be monitored. Anyone found to be abusing these conditions runs the risk of being towed or clamped.
